bug.summary: [integration_tests] Browser benchmarks fails due to node-pre-gyp and aws-sdk
bug.description:
Step to reproduce:
Checkout the tfjs (union) repo at head cd integration_tests yarn benchmark --layers
Notice the error message: 23 07 2019 10:54:53.444:ERROR [karma-server]: Error: Unable to resolve module [aws-sdk] from [.../tfjs/tfjs/integration_tests/node_modules/node-pre-gyp/lib/unpublish.js]

comments.comment: closing this as the related PR has been merged. Thank you
